  "description": "Hey folks, sorry for the delay in sending out an email. First, my laptop’s harddrive died, then the operating system I installed on the replacement drive was very very hard to use (laggy, glitchy,) and it’s only yesterday I got that replaced (with Debian 10, for the curious, and Fedora 33 was laggy and glitchy. Running KDE Plasma and first Gnome then LXDE on Fedora.)\nSince I had a few days without a computer around, I actually have written up the next couple letters I plan to send y’all by hand - expect them probably over the course of the day.\n",
